text: Saga Shrine Affiliation Shinto (佐嘉神社) is a Shinto shrine located in Saga, Kyushu. It is a Beppyo shrine, which means it is particularly notable in a certain way with a significant history. The shrine has two cannons at its entrance and was the traditional main shrine of the Saga Domain. It enshrines Daimyo and . It is the only Bekkaku Kanpeisha in Saga. == References == Category:Beppyo shrines Category:Bekkaku kanpeisha Category:Shinto shrines in Saga Prefecture
title: Saga Shrine
